msgctxt "an5.151:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.151:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga "
msgstr "16. The True Teaching "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.151:0.3"
msgid "151. Paṭhamasammattaniyāmasutta "
msgstr "151. Inevitability Regarding the Right Path (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.151:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with five qualities is unable to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities even when listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an5.151:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. VAR: kathikaṃ → kathitaṃ (mr)
#. VAR: ayoniso ca → ayoniso (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an5.151:1.3"
msgid "Kathaṃ paribhoti, kathikaṃ paribhoti, attānaṃ paribhoti, vikkhittacitto dhammaṃ suṇāti, anekaggacitto ayoniso ca manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They disparage the talk, the speaker, or themselves. They listen with distracted and scattered mind. They attend improperly. "

msgctxt "an5.151:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "Someone with these five qualities is unable to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities, even when listening to the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.175, sc2
msgctxt "an5.151:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "Someone with five qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an5.151:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.151:2.3"
msgid "Na kathaṃ paribhoti, na kathikaṃ paribhoti, na attānaṃ paribhoti, avikkhittacitto dhammaṃ suṇāti, ekaggacitto yoniso ca manasi karoti. "
msgstr "They don’t disparage the talk, the speaker, or themselves. They listen with undistracted and unified mind. They attend properly. "

msgctxt "an5.151:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattan”ti. "
msgstr "Someone with these five qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.151:2.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

